{
  "$comment": "Shared semantic spatial tokens for Unity + Three.js. Every state carries text + shape/icon + colour + accessible description — NEVER colour alone. Generate Unity constants and CSS/JS tokens from this file. v3: every coloured state carries a `color_family`, and `visual_profiles` gives each family an explicit, reviewed rendition per visual profile plus that profile's surface and contrast floors. The per-state `color` remains the DesktopDark rendition and the canonical identity; profile resolution never changes a state's meaning, only its rendition. Added for UX-01/UX-05/UX-09 (offline contrast audit).",
